<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <title>Beaufort AI — Maritime Intelligence</title>
  <script>
    // Redirect dashboard requests to local Pi
    if (window.location.pathname.includes('dashboard')) {
      window.location.href = 'http://192.168.1.226:5000/';
    }
  </script>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a3a52 0%, #0f2438 100%);
      color: #e0e0e0;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 20px;
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
    }
    .container {
      text-align: center;
      max-width: 600px;
    }
    h1 {
      font-size: 2.5em;
      color: #00d4ff;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      text-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.3);
    }
    p {
      font-size: 1.1em;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #aaa;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }
    .btn {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 12px 30px;
      background: #00d4ff;
      color: #0f2438;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 5px;
      font-weight: 600;
      transition: all 0.3s;
      margin: 10px;
    }
    .btn:hover {
      background: #00b4d9;
      transform: translateY(-2px);
    }
    .status {
      margin-top: 40px;
      padding: 20px;
      background: rgba(0, 212, 255, 0.1);
      border-left: 4px solid #00d4ff;
      text-align: left;
      border-radius: 5px;
    }
    .status-item {
      margin: 10px 0;
      font-family: monospace;
      font-size: 0.9em;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>⚓ BEAUFORT AI</h1>
    <p>Maritime Intelligence Platform</p>
    
    <p>Live sensor dashboard and storm prediction system for dynamic positioning vessels.</p>
    
    <div>
      <a href="http://192.168.1.226:5000/" class="btn">📊 Live Dashboard</a>
      <a href="/#about" class="btn">About</a>
      <a href="/#how" class="btn">How It Works</a>
    </div>
    
    <div class="status">
      <div class="status-item">✅ Live Dashboard: Online (192.168.1.226:5000)</div>
      <div class="status-item">✅ Sensor Network: 5 sensors active</div>
      <div class="status-item">✅ AI Model: Fine-tuning in progress</div>
      <div class="status-item">🔄 Website: Deploying to Cloudflare Pages</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
